<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>652</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bù yuàn zài kàn dào liú lèi de miàn kǒng,
 bù yuàn kàn dào xiāo yān mí màn de tiān kōng.
 kàn shǒu yuán zi de lǎo rén, ya ya xué yǔ de hái tóng,
 dōu shēn shēn de qī pàn, píng píng ān ān guò yī shēng.
 wèi shén me dì xiōng hèn dì xiōng,
 wèi shén me rén jiān tiān kōng zhàn zhēng bù tíng?
 wǒ xīn bù néng píng jìng, wǒ xīn bù néng píng jìng.
 wǒ yào jǔ shǒu qí dǎo hé píng. zhǔ
 rú guǒ nǐ bù zuò, wǒ jiù yī zhí qiú.
 zhí dào rén jiān dōu chōng mǎn nǐ de ài. zhǔ
 nǐ rú guǒ bù zuò, wǒ jiù yī zhí qiú.
 zhí dào shì jiè dōu chōng mǎn hé píng.</lyrics>
<title>qí dǎo hé píng 迦南652</title>
</song>